{"tid":1966012,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港被回歸 的原因！！！","createTime":"2020-04-10T00:49:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-10T12:09:17.000Z","uid":49784,"like":42,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"5d52be815277f83465e7f743066c261b2c51eab4","tid":1966012,"uid":49784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T00:49:13.000Z","msg":"當年 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">美國 蘇聯</span> 冷戰，軍備競賽<br />\n<br />\n適逢二戰過後，英美已經唔想再打仗，更何況打蘇聯？<br />\n<br />\n中國立場不未定，因為擁有核彈，立場足以左右整個結局<br />\n即使美國幫過中國打敗日本，中國不但冇感恩<br />\n反而要脅要拎返<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港</span>,先唔企蘇聯過邊<br />\n呢個&quot;交易&quot; 影響緊全球人類生命<br />\n核子冬天唔係咁易過<br />\n<br />\n因為中國唔想自己門口有英軍係到<br />\n即使英國唔想放手，但英美兩國計過數<br />\n如果英美 對 蘇中，第三次世界大戰係打唔過<br />\n<br />\n用腦諗下，英國用左成百年，<br />\n將香港由漁港變成國際金融中心<br />\n根據南京條約 香港係永久屬於英國<br />\n<br />\n有乜野原因要迫使英國送走咁大隻金蛋？<br />\n呢d &quot;回歸&quot; 對英國黎講，真係喪權辱國<br />\n<br />\n但有得揀咩？<br />\n美國都幫唔到手<br />\n<br />\n之後中國再做場戲比大家睇<br />\n一班愛國人士，學者，要求回歸<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ATkzAOQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FATkzAOQ.gif&h=857bef91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n彭定康，唔係先知，係有口難言<br />\n知得好清楚中國做緊乜<br />\n<br />\n百幾年嘅心血，會搵錢嘅金蛋，<br />\n英國真係咁情願送走？<br />\n<br />\n英國奶共<br />\n君子報仇，十年未晚<br />\n仲要講緊核彈，扮豬食老虎都要<br />\n<br />\n睇下呢個post<br />\n<br />\n戴卓爾夫人：英國恨不得永久擁有香港！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1965860\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1965860</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n英國係當香港掌上明珠<br />\n<br />\n香港係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">東方之珠</span>呀！！！<br />\n今日香港似乜野？<br />\n<br />\n係邊個造成？<br />\n點會係英國呀？<br />\n<br />\n認清邊個係後底乸啦<br />\n<br />\n以下將會有極大量三毛追擊 會話<br />\n英國無冇，奶共<br />\n引起罵戰<br />\n分散討論<br />\n<br />\n捱到今日，要靠大家<br />\n將來都係大家，共勉之<br />\n<br />\n如果大家可以share 呢個post 就好<br />\n因為仲有好多人唔知<br />\n<br />\n網上可以搵到有關評論"},{"pid":"ae4bef4b9c677d47ac6ebb566e7eb4b21ab74745","tid":1966012,"uid":49784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T00:50:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f2afe050b1eabad9a9077b41113735de6ce9f61","tid":1966012,"uid":141703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T00:51:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35a0333736c9ef11fa87357b72b1f0c095b115ba","tid":1966012,"uid":268373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T00:52:47.000Z","msg":"Agger"},{"pid":"206893a32cf9a66bb01117cb80504765eda7b305","tid":1966012,"uid":49784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T00:54:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0cd6897901391f400d04035523749fbb6088b3b","tid":1966012,"uid":49784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T00:55:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47ea7fb5dcd0defe50d6687480a0ce73565eeca6","tid":1966012,"uid":49784,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T00:57:53.000Z","msg":"比你地有間鋪係銅鑼灣收租，你都唔會送比中國啦？<br />\n<br />\n講緊成個香港咁送？"},{"pid":"923955fba2b7ce4ab0a21ef3259179dbc910307b","tid":1966012,"uid":49784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T00:58:35.000Z","msg":"三毛唔敢推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"446e0813b5173bb28cf432139a8b80aa3f07e5e5","tid":1966012,"uid":19549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T01:01:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5ce7b66561fc1ec9da67d0aedbfd3be0ccab90b","tid":1966012,"uid":209248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T01:01:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1f75237e3b64045161c7f1635de444c7f8eff53","tid":1966012,"uid":49784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T01:04:40.000Z","msg":"如果可以，希望大家幫手推上去，比多d 人知"},{"pid":"fdced3f144aea50451d72eabc3a82b6553c91890","tid":1966012,"uid":149026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T01:06:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1a7a3ead59e2826c83cca8d04d401beb7643cdba","tid":1966012,"uid":195166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T01:09:01.000Z","msg":"黃之鋒、敖卓軒：港澳不算殖民地？1972年聯合國決議的真相｜觀點｜端傳媒 Initium Media <a href=\"https://theinitium.com/article/20161102-opinion-joshuawong-jeffreyngo-hongkong/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftheinitium.com%2Farticle%2F20161102-opinion-joshuawong-jeffreyngo-hongkong%2F&d=GkP5J4C4AUyWsqXHyTPi6wg0DHywPMniAnH04N%2BeXdM%3D&h=9905ffd0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://theinitium.com/article/20161102-opinion-joshuawong-jeffreyngo-hongkong/</a>"},{"pid":"5c7cfda93daecd7abf1ee0594efca540a27153ad","tid":1966012,"uid":49784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T01:21:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa99ffa2c600c53d4910e555bb4ddb4d02532e99","tid":1966012,"uid":64120,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T01:23:31.000Z","msg":"似乎太過簡化<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過都推 冷戰的確係遠因"},{"pid":"37614e297a7cea9dc13e88e8db70ea92f0820e5b","tid":1966012,"uid":231563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T01:29:14.000Z","msg":"剩係比香港島<br />\n停你水路、冇飛機，點生存<br />\n求其送返一千幾百億比你，幫手做場戲。"},{"pid":"d7eebc229bd8086b0903cb278fcafc479aa7e443","tid":1966012,"uid":275903,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T01:29:57.000Z","msg":"現實就係<br />\n當美國佬係一九年下半年時 想吹雞圍屌中共時<br />\n英國佬繼續雪雪聲 又或者想兩邊奶  當黑警闖入英國領事官邸時 又默不出聲  連鄭文傑被送中 都係口交兩句算數<br />\n不如你打破幻想 英國佬根本唔在乎香港變成點，唔係首相有武肺 我包保華為登陸硬英國 <br />\n我對英國近乎死心 只希望佢唔好拖美國佬後腿 就已經還得神落"},{"pid":"6ba3993ace9d0b1e2e4af6007dda9303a2d2e89a","tid":1966012,"uid":197956,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T01:35:52.000Z","msg":"首先你要明白一樣重要既野：<br />\n香港係仆街英國出賣俾中國。英國多次想用香港交換利益。<br />\n無錯香港既港督係幾好，但老家仆街係事實。<br />\n你睇下係邊條仆街首先承認老共？又係邊個係老美反中國5G時仲要用中共5G?<br />\n英國佬作為海盜後代，賊性不改。你估佢地真係道德高尚？點解美國會有解放戰爭？老美同情香港我信，但英國佬？其實佢仲仆街過老共，唔好仇人當恩人。"},{"pid":"dc07a4e1ac9398ab8108020550795947099b5d01","tid":1966012,"uid":66686,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T01:38:37.000Z","msg":"仲有就係一出口就話&quot;港人&quot;支持&quot;民主回歸&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明民調得半成人支持<br />\n九成反對主權移交<br />\n合理化&quot;回歸&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明係用武力迫<br />\n無民意支持"},{"pid":"0ad97842e979815cb273751ec7418767b7c1fe64","tid":1966012,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T01:39:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"434daa35ad0016a92e3b58473a3a23d9c8e2f158","tid":1966012,"uid":261873,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T01:42:21.000Z","msg":"連BNO居英權都冇<br />\n點叫人奶英"},{"pid":"bda2b39d8c8301eaedd3f2896037fa7777ce029c","tid":1966012,"uid":49784,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dc07a4e1ac9398ab8108020550795947099b5d01","tid":1966012,"uid":66686,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T01:38:37.000Z","msg":"仲有就係一出口就話&quot;港人&quot;支持&quot;民主回歸&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明民調得半成人支持<br />\n九成反對主權移交<br />\n合理化&quot;回歸&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明係用武力迫<br />\n無民意支持"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T01:54:00.000Z","msg":"根本戲一場"},{"pid":"67de497645e47012c9115eb8427ade7ad60a05bc","tid":1966012,"uid":60177,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"47ea7fb5dcd0defe50d6687480a0ce73565eeca6","tid":1966012,"uid":49784,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T00:57:53.000Z","msg":"比你地有間鋪係銅鑼灣收租，你都唔會送比中國啦？<br />\n<br />\n講緊成個香港咁送？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T02:00:22.000Z","msg":"事實上送咗就係送<br />\n當年仲要有乜鳩歸還殖民地嘅思潮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e909e0f1ff62536ca31d3c8f3ac582b69bbb988","tid":1966012,"uid":49784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T03:02:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca91a10a04b1ab94351018e92f9514736690fb01","tid":1966012,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T03:06:00.000Z","msg":"好文<br />\n推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"e1f75237e3b64045161c7f1635de444c7f8eff53","tid":1966012,"uid":49784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T01:04:40.000Z","msg":"如果可以，希望大家幫手推上去，比多d 人知"}}